OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FEarly mist, patchy fog or low
OL,6,Fcloud will disperse leaving bright
OL,7,Fconditions as high cloud increases.
OL,8,FChance of an afternoon shower. Rather
OL,9,Fwarm for many places, cooler along the
OL,10,Fcoast.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FCloudy with isolated light
OL,13,Fshowers to start, breaks in the cloud
OL,14,Flater could see some fog patches
OL,15,Fdevelop around dawn. Winds remain
OL,16,Flight and temperatures mild overnight.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
