OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CMonday:FBright spells and scattered
OL,6,Fheavy showers developing mainly across
OL,7,Fthe north of the region. Low cloud
OL,8,Fwill spread westwards through the
OL,9,Fregion overnight.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:
OL,12,FTuesday and Wednesday dry with bright
OL,13,For sunny spells, but perhaps coastal
OL,14,Flow cloud for Tuesday. Thursday long
OL,15,Fsunny spells but breezy. Temperatures
OL,16,Fgenerally near average inland.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
